WEBVTT

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:31.360
ulipobadilisha mtazamo wangu
kuhusu hedhi milele.

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:37.736
Mwaka 2009, mimi na Tuhin tulikuwa 
tunasoma stashada katika ubunifu.

00:04:37.760 --> 00:04:39.416
Tukapendana

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:41.880
na nilikuwa huru
kujadiliana naye kuhusu siku zangu.

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:44.560
Tuhin alijua kidogo kuhusu siku.

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:47.800
(Kicheko)

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:55.416
Alishangazwa kujua kwamba
wasichana hupata maumivu makali

00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:56.856
na hutokwa damu kila mwezi.

00:04:56.880 --> 00:04:58.976
(Kicheko)

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:00.496
Ndio.